      • addComment

        public void addComment(String path,
                       String... commentLines)
        Adds a comment just before the specified path. The comment can be multiple lines. An empty string will indicate a blank line.
        Parameters:
        path - Configuration path to add comment.
        commentLines - Comments to add. One String per line.
